developer.name: Alveo Land
developer.seo_title: Alveo Land Corp. Projects For Sale | Instahomes
developer.seo_desc: As a subsidiary of Ayala Land, Alveo Land builds beautiful residential, business, commercial, and leisure developments across the Philippines | Instahomes
developer.short_desc: Alveo Land caters to the upscale market with its dynamic portfolio of residential, business, commercial, and leisure developments across the country.
developer.overview:
A subsidiary of Ayala Land, Alveo offers a vibrant portfolio of groundbreaking real estate developments that provides upscale living and working spaces within various thriving and emerging growth centers around the country. 

Armed with sharper foresight, unparalleled excellence, total commitment, and an inherent passion and drive for innovation, the company is committed to providing thoughtfully-designed and master planned living environments for the unique needs of its discerning market.
developer.values_description:
Alveo Land strives to elevate our customers’ quality of life through innovative real estate solutions in vibrant growth centers all over the country.

It acts responsibly with integrity, accountability and total commitment.

It achieves excellence through passion, focus and foresight.

development.name: The Lattice at Parklinks
development.seo_title: The Lattice at Parklinks Condos For Sale | Alveo Land
development.seo_desc: The Lattice is a condo in Parklinks, a 35-hectare mixed-used development in C-5 with condos for sale in beautiful landscapes and sceneries. | Instahomes
development.short_desc: The Lattice is a condo in Parklinks, a 35-hectare mixed-used development, and the biggest estate in C-5 with beautiful in-house landscapes and sceneries.
development.location: C-5 Road, Brgy. Rosario, Pasig City
development.overview:
The Lattice is Alveo Land's first upscale residential tower in Parklinks. Parklinks is a 35-hectare mixed-used development and the biggest estate along the prime C-5 corridor. 

It is envisioned to be the greenest urban estate in Metro Manila dedicating 50% of the development to open spaces and greeneries. It services upscale high-class living in the urban lands of the metro and offers a wide selection of unit spaces suited for the modern man.
development.description_by_car: Accessible via C-5, Ortigas Avenue and Amang Rodriguez avenue with future access to Circulo Verde and Metropoli.
development.description_by_commute: From the I.P.I Bus Stop, take the Cainta-Quiapo to Taytay- Quiapo via Ortigas Avenue Manila East Road.
development.area_facts:
Schools: Creative Beginners, Leap School for Young Children, Petite Graine, Informatics College, Thames International School of Asia
Hospitals: The Medical City Clinic, Fun Ranch Clinic, The Medical City, Rosario Specialist Clinic, Manggahan Health Center
Places of Worship: Faith Heritage Christian Church, Christ the King Parish, The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, The Philippine Centre for St. Pio of Pietrelcina, The Call
Malls: All Day Super Market, Rustan's Supermarket, Sänti's Delicatessen, Cyber and Fashion Mall, Eastwood City Walk
development.amenity_1_desc: Enjoy intimate parties at the convenience of home. Make your celebration extra special with the Lattice.
development.amenity_2_desc: Get the wellness you deserve with the state-of-the-art equipments available in the Lattice' exclusive gym.
development.amenity_3_desc: Bathe in the beautiful paradise spaces without the need to go far from home. Enjoy the Lattice' grand pool and spa.

seo_title: The Lattice Parklinks Studio Condo For Sale | Alveo Land
seo_desc: The Studio Unit of the Lattice at Parklinks strikes a great balance of elegance and comfort for young individuals at C-5, Pasig City. | Instahomes
overview:
The Studio Unit of the Lattice strikes a great balance of elegance and comfort for young individuals at the heart of C-5, Pasig city being the largest in Parklinks.

Parklinks is envisioned to be the greenest urban estate in Metro Manila dedicating 50% of the development to open spaces and greeneries. It services upscale high-class living in the urban lands of the metro and offers a wide selection of unit spaces suited for the modern man.
property_details:
Refined finish where the Living, Dining, Kitchen, and Balcony are  built with 600x600mm porcelain tile floors, while the Bedroom has Wood Laminated Flooring. All parts of the unit have paint finished ceilings and walls.
